pull.title: Remove TransactionTableModel::TxIDRole
pull.body: The role `TxIDRole` is a duplicate of `TxHashRole`. This change favours `TxHashRole`.

events.body: utACK - I think it was duplicated because TxID used to contain the vout id at some point, too.

See travis report:
```
qt/transactionfilterproxy.cpp: In member function ‘virtual bool TransactionFilterProxy::filterAcceptsRow(int, const QModelIndex&) const’:
qt/transactionfilterproxy.cpp:39:31: error: ‘TxIDRole’ is not a member of ‘TransactionTableModel’
     QString txid = index.data(TransactionTableModel::TxIDRole).toString();
```
